# Getting Started with Retrofit
# URL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R4XU8yPzSx0&list=PLpUMhvC6l7APq7y_FFfK-GEHvcUKqo6SC&index=1
# Problem: List down open-source GitHub repos.
# Steps:
1) Add permission for Internet in Menifest
2) Add Retrofit dependancy in app.gradle
3) Create Model class
4) Create Retrofit Client interface
5) Create Adapter for list
6) Create Class and layout from which api call will made
    1) Create Retrofit Builder object with baseUrl and GsonConverterFactory
    2) Create Retrofit Object
    3) Create Api client object
    4) Call api method from Api client object
    5) Actual call api with Callback object
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
